latestPosts.caption:
I walked up to @motwayne at the iReel awards in 2018, introduced myself and told him I will work with him in the next 5 years. He said “cool” in his classic style. 

On 30th July 2022 (well within 5 years) this happened. Landing and closing jokes with @avinashsampath later, I started writing dialogues for this MAD movie. 

I have told this story a million times at the @andolanofficial office with a patient @jasssipinkman being enthusiastic every time I repeat it but it still doesn’t get old. 

Thank you for this. Full njoyment. And now we laugh at “31st Jan draft” part as if that was the last draft.

@aryaamenon @pratik8shah @nirali.n @vijesh.plexus @yashoda.plexus @ishikamohanmotwane @ananyapanday @vihaansamat @devikavatsa
